Text: Re years is too longTurns out that I probably wont be down until after the new year Hope all is going well with you Ive been reading the news and I hope this Dynergy thing works out well for you Have a good trip to London Best Charlie Original Message From To Charles ecuruscvcom Sent Monday November PM Subject RE years is too long Hi Charlie Are you coming down to my sunny and hot part of the country Let me know soon as I may be in London for a few days after thanksgiving Regards Jeff Original Message From Charles Jones Charles ecuruscvcomENRON Sent Tuesday October AM To Shankman Jeffrey A Subject RE years is too long Hey Jeff Hope youre hanging in there buddy It was exciting to exchange email months ago but predictably we fell out of touch Im trying to swing a biz trip to Houston at the end of November If it develops Ill be sure to give you a shout Best Charlie This email is the property of Enron Corp andor its relevant affiliate and may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient s Any review use distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited If you are not the intended recipient or authorized to receive for the recipient please contact the sender or reply to Enron Corp at and delete all copies of the message This email and any attachments hereto are not intended to be an offer or an acceptance and do not create or evidence a binding and enforceable contract between Enron Corp or any of its affiliates and the intended recipient or any other party and may not be relied on by anyone as the basis of a contract by estoppel or otherwise Thank you
